name: Astrobone Internal Structure
description: During the great world war there is one giant machine that is responsible for most of deaths and destruction, it's name is Robobone. After the war, the body of Robobone was disambled and lock away as it's too destructive and dangereous. But one of the lead scientist sneakily steal it's core energy and AI, and install it to an android in a shape of a boy. And call him Astrobone.
